[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/ice_beam">Ice Beam</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/ice_beam">Ice Beam</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The foe is struck with an icy-cold beam of energy. It may also freeze the target solid.</p>